Version 0.0.3 notes (June 16, 2016)
-----------------------------------

Python 3 support added by Andrew White (https://github.com/andrewmwhite).

Version 0.0.2 notes (August 28, 2011)
-------------------------------------

Changed setup.py to have Github URLs for home page and download. Added
.gitignore.

Version 0.0.1 notes (August 27, 2011)
-------------------------------------

Initial release.  This code has been in production use for a couple of
years, so despite its version number it should be considered fairly safe to
use.

